query:
UPDATE tasks
               SET github_issue_repo_id = $2,
                   github_issue_number = $3,
                   github_issue_url = $4,
                   github_issue_state = $5,
                   github_issue_assignee = $6,
                   github_issue_synced_at = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
                   updated_at = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
               WHERE id = $1
